.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>时间:上午第二节历史课<br>相关人员:水哥，李少，paipai，历史老师</p></blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"事件过程\"><a href=\"#事件过程\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"事件过程\"></a>事件过程</h2><p>十班男生在后方空荡区域水枪对射，在历史课上课后，水哥意图向<u>李少</u>射击水枪。但因水枪准度受限，导致其射偏至paipai。在作案过程中，被历史老师发现，其说到：“这种事情我教书这么多年从未碰到。都<strong>高中生</strong>了还玩这种幼稚的东西“。水哥道歉并在接下来的课程中<strong>安分守己</strong>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"事件影响\"><a href=\"#事件影响\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"事件影响\"></a>事件影响</h2><p>无较大影响，男生称水哥在上课<del>打手枪</del>。</p>\n","text":"上海市闵行中学高一十班爆发水枪门事件 时间:上午第二节历史课相关人员:水哥，李少，paipai，历史老师 事件过程十班男生在后方空荡区域水枪对射，在历史课上课后，水哥意图向李少射击水枪。但因水枪准度受限，导致其射偏至paipai。在作案过程中，被历史老师发现，其说到：“这种事情我...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":217,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"日常","slug":"日常","count":1,"path":"api/tags/日常.json"},{"name":"班级","slug":"班级","count":1,"path":"api/tags/班级.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E5%B8%82%E9%97%B5%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%A6%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%81%E7%8F%AD%E7%88%86%E5%8F%91%E6%B0%B4%E6%9E%AA%E9%97%A8%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">上海市闵行中学高一十班爆发水枪门事件</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">事件过程</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">事件影响</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"MuskZhou","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://aboutme.paipai.site/paipai.jpg","link":"/","description":"一个创始于博主16岁生日的小站","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"github":{"icon":"/svg/github.svg","link":"https://github.com/MuskZhouMQ"},"twitter":{"icon":"/svg/twitter.svg","link":"https://twitter.com/TUF_Pai"},"QQ":{"icon":"/svg/